\id HAG - Biblica® Open Luganda Contemporary Bible 2014 
\h Kaggayi 
\toc1 Kaggayi 
\toc2 Kaggayi 
\toc3 Kag 
\mt2 Ekitabo Ekiyitibwa 
\mt1 Kaggayi 
\c 1  
\s1 Okukoowoola olw’Okuddaabiriza Ennyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* 
\p  
\v 1 Mu mwaka ogwokubiri ogw’okufuga kwa kabaka Daliyo, ku lunaku olusooka mu mwezi ogw’omukaaga, ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira nnabbi Kaggayi okutegeeza Zerubbaberi mutabani wa Seyalutyeri, ow’essaza lya Yuda, ne Yoswa mutabani wa Yekozadaaki kabona asinga obukulu nti: 
\p  
\v 2 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’eggye nti, “Abantu bano boogera nti, ‘Ekiseera tekinnatuuka okuddaabiriza ennyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd*.’ ” 
\p  
\v 3 Awo ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira nnabbi Kaggayi nga kyogera nti;  
\v 4 “Kino kye kiseera mmwe okubeera mu nnyumba zammwe enkole obulungi, naye ennyumba eyo n’erekebwa nga kifulukwa?” 
\p  
\v 5 Kale nno bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye nti, “Mweddeko ku neeyisa yammwe.  
\v 6 Musimbye bingi naye ne mukungula bitono; mulya naye temukkuta; munywa naye ennyonta tebaggwaako; mwambala naye temubuguma; mukolera empeera naye ze mukoze muziteeka mu nsawo ejjudde ebituli.” 
\p  
\v 7 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye nti, “Mweddeko ku neeyisa yammwe.  
\v 8 Mwambuke mu nsozi muleeteyo embaawo muzimbe ennyumba ngisanyukire, ngulumizibwe,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 9 “Mwasuubira bingi, naye mulaba bwe muvuddemu ebitono. Bye mwaleeta eka, nabifuumuula. Mumanyi ensonga? bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye. Kubanga buli muntu afa ku nnyumba ye naye ennyumba yange mugigayaaliridde.  
\v 10 Eggulu kyerivudde liziyizibwa okuleeta omusulo, n’ettaka n’okuleeta ne litaleeta bibala byalyo.  
\v 11 Nasindika ekyeya ku nnimiro ne ku nsozi, ku mmere ey’empeke ne ku wayini omuggya, ku mafuta ne ku buli bibala eby’ettaka, ku bantu ne ku nsolo, ne ku mirimu gyonna egy’engalo.” 
\b  
\p  
\v 12 Awo Zerubbaberi mutabani wa Seyalutyeri, ne Yoswa mutabani wa Yekozadaaki, ye yali kabona asinga obukulu, n’abantu bonna abaasigalawo ne bagondera eddoboozi lya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waabwe, n’obubaka bwa nnabbi Kaggayi, kubanga \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waabwe ye yamutuma. Abantu ne batya \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 13 Awo Kaggayi omubaka wa \nd Mukama\nd* n’ategeeza abantu obubaka obwava eri \nd Mukama\nd* nti, “Ndi wamu nammwe,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 14 Awo \nd Mukama\nd* n’akubiriza omutima gwa Zerubbaberi mutabani wa Seyalutyeri, ow’essaza lya Yuda, n’omutima gwa Yoswa mutabani wa Yekozadaaki, kabona asinga obukulu, n’emitima egy’abantu bonna abaasigalawo, ne bajja ne batandika omulimu ku nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda waabwe,  
\v 15 ku lunaku olw’amakumi abiri mu ennya mu mwezi ogw’omukaaga mu mwaka ogwokubiri ogw’okufuga kwa kabaka Daliyo. 
\c 2  
\s1 Ekitiibwa Ekyasuubizibwa eky’Ennyumba Empya 
\p  
\v 1 Awo ku lunaku olw’amakumi abiri mu olumu mu mwezi ogw’omusanvu, ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira nnabbi Kaggayi nti,  
\v 2 “Yogera ne Zerubbaberi mutabani wa Seyalutyeri, ow’essaza lya Yuda ne Yoswa mutabani wa Yekozadaaki kabona asinga obukulu, n’abantu abaasigalawo, obabuuze nti,  
\v 3 ‘Ani mu mmwe akyasigaddewo eyalaba ku kitiibwa ky’ennyumba eno? Ebafaananira etya kaakano? Tebafaananira ng’eteriimu kaabuntu?  
\v 4 Kale nno guma omwoyo, ggwe Zerubbaberi, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*; guma omwoyo, ggwe Yoswa mutabani wa Yekozadaaki kabona asinga obukulu; mugume omwoyo mmwe mwenna abantu ab’omu nsi,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, ‘Mukole, kubanga ndi wamu nammwe,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye.  
\v 5 ‘Kino kye nalagaana nammwe bwe mwali muva mu Misiri, ng’Omwoyo wange anaabeeranga nammwe. Temutya.’ 
\p  
\v 6 “Bw’atyo bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye nti, ‘Mu bbanga eritali ly’ewala ndikankanya eggulu n’ensi, n’ennyanja n’olukalu.  
\v 7 Ndikankanya amawanga gonna, n’amawanga gonna ge njagala galijja, ne nzijuza ennyumba eno ekitiibwa,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye.  
\v 8 ‘Effeeza yange, ne zaabu yange,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’eggye.  
\v 9 ‘Ekitiibwa eky’ennyumba eriwo kaakano, kirisinga ekitiibwa ky’eri eyasooka era mu kifo kino ndizzaawo emirembe,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye.” 
\s1 Okubuulirira n’Okusuubiza 
\p  
\v 10 Awo ku lunaku olw’amakumi abiri mu ennya olw’omwezi ogw’omwenda mu mwaka ogwokubiri ogw’okufuga kwa Daliyo, ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira nnabbi Kaggayi nti,  
\v 11 “Bw’atyo bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye nti, ‘Buuza bakabona etteeka kye ligamba.  
\v 12 Omuntu bw’asitulira ennyama eyatukuzibwa mu kirenge eky’ekyambalo kye, ekirenge ne kikoma ku mugaati oba ku supu, oba ku wayini, oba ku mafuta oba ku mmere endala yonna, bitukuzibwa?’ ” 
\p Bakabona ne baddamu nti, “Nedda.” 
\p  
\v 13 Awo Kaggayi n’abuuza nti, “Omuntu atali mulongoofu olw’omulambo, bw’akoma ku bintu ebyo, bifuuka ebitali birongoofu?” 
\p Bakabona ne baddamu nti, “Bifuuka ebitali birongoofu.” 
\p  
\v 14 Kaggayi n’addamu nti, “Kale nno bwe batyo bwe bali abantu bano n’eggwanga lino. Buli kye bakola ne buli kye bawaayo ng’ekiweebwayo, si kirongoofu,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 15 “ ‘Kale nno, mweddeko okuva ku lunaku lwa leero, mujjukire ebiseera biri bwe byali, nga n’ejjinja erimu terinnateekebwa ku linnaalyo mu yeekaalu ya \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 16 Omuntu yenna bwe yatuukanga ku ntuumu eyandibadde ey’ebipimo amakumi abiri, yassangawo ebipimo kkumi. Omuntu yenna bwe yalaganga mu ssogolero okusenamu lita amakumi ataano, yasangangamu amakumi abiri.  
\v 17 Nakolimira emirimu gyonna egy’emikono gyammwe n’okugengewala n’obukuku, n’omuzira, naye ne mutakyuka kudda gye ndi,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 18 Okuva olunaku lwa leero, olw’amakumi abiri mu ennya mu mwezi ogw’omwenda, mujjukire olunaku lwe baazimba omusingi gwa yeekaalu ya \nd Mukama\nd*. Mwebuuze nti,  
\v 19 Wakyaliwo ensigo eyasigala mu tterekero? Mulabe, emiti gino egimenyeddwa, ogw’omuzabbibu n’ogw’omutiini, n’ogw’omukomamawanga, n’ogw’omuzeeyituuni tegibalangako bibala. 
\p “ ‘Naye okuva ne leero ndibawa omukisa.’ ” 
\p  
\v 20 Awo ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira Kaggayi omulundi ogwokubiri ku lunaku olw’amakumi abiri mu ennya olw’omwezi ogwo nga kigamba nti,  
\v 21 “Tegeeza Zerubbaberi gavana wa Yuda nti ndikankanya eggulu n’ensi.  
\v 22 Ndisulika entebe ez’obwakabaka ne nzigyawo obuyinza bw’obwakabaka obunnaggwanga. Ndiwamba amagaali n’abavuzi baago, n’embalaasi na buli abazeebagala, balittibwa baganda baabwe. 
\p  
\v 23 “ ‘Ku lunaku olwo, ggwe omuweereza wange Zerubbaberi mutabani wa Seyalutyeri, ndikufuula ng’akabonero, kubanga nkulonze,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye.”